      <text bytes="69124" xml:space="preserve">{{short description|Supranational court in Strasbourg, France, established by the European Convention on Human Rights}}
{{distinguish|text=the [[Court of Justice of the European Union]], the highest court of the European Union}}
{{Use dmy dates|date=July 2020}}
